' VBA Loops_Conditionals overview
' -----------------------------------------
'
' Purpose:
' - Enable decision-making and repetition in VBA code.
'
' Main structures:
' 1. If / ElseIf / Else
' 2. Select Case
' 3. For loop (fixed iteration)
' 4. For Each loop (collection iteration)
' 5. Do While loop (condition at top)
' 6. Do Until loop (condition at top)
'
' Best practices:
' - Choose If / ElseIf for simple conditions.
' - Use Select Case for multi-value branching.
' - Prefer For Each when iterating objects or collections.
' - Avoid infinite loops by ensuring loop exit conditions.
'
' -----------------------------------------
